n<br />\n唔得牙?<br />\n同<br />\n唔得呀!<br />\n根本係兩回事</blockquote><br />\n( Show Blocked User - 鳩UP大笨象 )<br />\n大量文盲mk進駐連登打5p字仲自覺冇問題"},{"pid":"5c75730274f6491aa27b5ec3d0e02c07a1003dc1","tid":175894,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad14feb1d4950dc3c9f7b0e47ee649875917813","tid":175894,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時用開速成<br />\n2個口打個唔字真係好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過牙字會睇情況用<br />\n例如我會打&quot;你仲唔訓教牙？&quot;<br />\n而唔會打&quot;你仲唔訓教呀？&quot;<br />\n但就從來無打過挽字，無乜幾何會用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牙你老母咩<br />\n仲夠膽講出黎</blockquote><br />\n讀一次嘅話<br />\n兩句好似有語氣上嘅分別？<br />\n牙低音啲 呀高音啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀我係讀音撚</blockquote><br />\n你係5p撚</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁，牙同呀讀音上跟本唔同用法。<br />\n唔知你真膠定假膠，不過唔好成日見人用牙就話人5p啦</blockquote><br />\n其實我都唔明點解當「牙」先係正確讀音嗰陣都要用「呀」咁笨柒<br />\n<br />\n唔得牙?<br />\n同<br />\n唔得呀!<br />\n根本係兩回事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一隻字唔只得一個音，我都知有分別，所以咪比你用標點黎表達個分別囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77ad07fcc7e792f096077d8f3247eb2e2568f0a","tid":175894,"uid":42625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪低撚能㗎，成班小學都無讀過<br />\n<br />\n玩 做名詞 時就讀'換',  玩具，遊玩<br />\n玩 做動詞 就讀 '挽' , 玩遊戲</blockquote><br />\n其實唔係讀 挽<br />\n玩係waan2<br />\n挽係waan5<br />\n係有分別</blockquote><br />\n巴打你係少數耳仔無問題嘅人<br />\n根本聲調就唔同，但係上面成堆人話係一樣音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cdfe87688a52346dc97357465a723aad668cb4","tid":175894,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"終於進化到屌5P字會比人屌番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bea88ad91a97b90e86a1a7de960525afb3a3dc","tid":175894,"uid":42625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於進化到屌5P字會比人屌番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要聲大大仲要話係一樣<br />\n屌人未讀過小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n笑到我痴線 果然無知係最幸福最有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ffb49b10010bbb102aa7964f9b3715825030ad","tid":175894,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾畀被比</blockquote><br />\n點分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5834dce2b65ac501b67f87efbf53fb64018024","tid":175894,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾畀被比</blockquote><br />\n點分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畀：給予，例：我畀啲野你<br />\n俾：准許、容許，例：唔好俾佢走<br />\n比：比較，例：我比你高<br />\n被：被動式，例：我被人打，佢老母被狗屌"},{"pid":"2f02f05ac6aaf4433db4f3f7d8dd7dfa8066fb91","tid":175894,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"7f9374c4941eca5adc5884f672999867b3656dae","tid":175894,"uid":90108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>系</blockquote><br />\n你打個系字出黎一陣又俾人炮轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909fca78024ebbe4d80a0a7aa31375b600b64be6","tid":175894,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:27:31.000Z","msg":"咁多個5p字入面個挽字真係最撚扯火"},{"pid":"b1b26c2e8274b91c4ddd8120aebc07158381bad9","tid":175894,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T07:59:29.000Z","msg":"d 5p字根本係講廣東省班人用開既<br />\n根本就唔係咩5p字"},{"pid":"91c7276f5d1ee7b80c5400de3f7594d2f5b441b0","tid":175894,"uid":38648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同字讀音唔同，睇上文下理咪睇得出囉，洗鬼打讀音咩<br />\n<br />\n唔通「中間」同「中獎」個中字讀音唔同，咁就要打成 「鐘間」或者「縱獎」咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd中學雞成日話中文係死亡之卷，有無諗過其實係自己d中文水平低到仆街</blockquote><br />\ndse係考中文常識嘅就唔會死咁多人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過會死一大班5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n(香港語言學學會)\t粵音\t漢字<br />\nngaa4\t\t牙, 吾, 琊, 岈, 伢, 枒, 蚜, 衙, 芽, 玡<br />\n<br />\n(香港語言學學會)\t粵音\t漢字<br />\naa4\t\t啊<br />\n<br />\n呀\t<br />\naa1 同音字 孲, 錏, 鴉 \t\t<br />\nhaa1 同音字 颬, 蝦, 岈<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=66df07f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/</a><br />\n<br />\n「中」字係真係有兩個讀音,<br />\n但請上面班dse中文好勁既巴打提供一下source證明呀字可以讀做「牙」"},{"pid":"24fd715e0e018c5fcee148cfcc20e1fcbd05db03","tid":175894,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"吾系甘牙"},{"pid":"5bbbd40ad258ebd31df0622677d18116e98edb64","tid":175894,"uid":43202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但其實玩讀到挽嘅音?.?</blockquote><br />\n有冇讀書?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AA%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25AA%25B1&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=92cf7141\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AA%B1</a><br />\n邊撚個無讀過書呀柒頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係你就捐返入你老母個臭閪喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁兩個字既讀音夠唔係waan2<br />\n但係意思上就有分別<br />\n例如你問人 係咪玩嘢啊/你玩緊乜<br />\n你用。個挽字意思上就已經唔同啦</blockquote><br />\n縮左入你老母個臭閪度?唔出聲既</blockquote><br />\n我而家係話玩讀唔撚到挽(我地平時講嗰個音)你而家串柒柒咁話讀到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔撚識聲調就查啦傻閪，你睇下waan5係咪平時讀法？<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AE%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25AE%25BE&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c3a3284a\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AE%BE</a>link都比撚埋你個弱智狗呀。我而家無撚問你意思上係點，我係問鳩緊你讀音姐on9仔我自己不嬲用玩，本身打算理性討論下點知你個傻鳩係要沖出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895661d632d1b213b419c744305c93a43b1b2869","tid":175894,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T15:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於進化到屌5P字會比人屌番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ee3cf3ce5dfaf9874876fb7e36ac95aae2488c","tid":175894,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T23:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但其實玩讀到挽嘅音?.?</blockquote><br />\n有冇讀書?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AA%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25AA%25B1&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=92cf7141\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AA%B1</a><br />\n邊撚個無讀過書呀柒頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係你就捐返入你老母個臭閪喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁兩個字既讀音夠唔係waan2<br />\n但係意思上就有分別<br />\n例如你問人 係咪玩嘢啊/你玩緊乜<br />\n你用。個挽字意思上就已經唔同啦</blockquote><br />\n縮左入你老母個臭閪度?唔出聲既</blockquote><br />\n我而家係話玩讀唔撚到挽(我地平時講嗰個音)<span style=\"color: red;\">你而家串柒柒咁話讀到喎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔撚識聲調就查啦傻閪，你睇下waan5係咪平時讀法？<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AE%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25AE%25BE&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c3a3284a\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AE%BE</a>link都比撚埋你個弱智狗呀。我而家無撚問你意思上係點，我係問鳩緊你讀音姐on9仔我自己不嬲用玩，本身打算理性討論下點知你個傻鳩係要沖出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊一句有咁既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問你有冇讀書係想知你點解咁都問得出咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93173ab158308e52207c8e2d7550f336e0bc7e1e","tid":175894,"uid":28895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>系</blockquote><br />\n你打個系字出黎一陣又俾人炮轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己5p講到自己好撚有道理咁<br />\n咩世界"},{"pid":"25f8b07ed2bdf9f43ea4cc38d388516b79568e83","tid":175894,"uid":28895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但其實玩讀到挽嘅音?.?</blockquote><br />\n有冇讀書?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AA%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25AA%25B1&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=92cf7141\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AA%B1</a><br />\n邊撚個無讀過書呀柒頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係你就捐返入你老母個臭閪喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁兩個字既讀音夠唔係waan2<br />\n但係意思上就有分別<br />\n例如你問人 係咪玩嘢啊/你玩緊乜<br />\n你用。個挽字意思上就已經唔同啦</blockquote><br />\n縮左入你老母個臭閪度?唔出聲既</blockquote><br />\n我而家係話玩讀唔撚到挽(我地平時講嗰個音)你而家串柒柒咁話讀到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔撚識聲調就查啦傻閪，你睇下waan5係咪平時讀法？<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AE%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2Fsearch.php%3Fq%3D%25AE%25BE&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c3a3284a\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/search.php?q=%AE%BE</a>link都比撚埋你個弱智狗呀。我而家無撚問你意思上係點，我係問鳩緊你讀音姐on9仔我自己不嬲用玩，本身打算理性討論下點知你個傻鳩係要沖出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 你柒少陣先啦表情撚&quot;?.?&quot;<br />\n2. 宜家不嬲討論個點係班5p將個玩打左做挽，講緊兩個字既意思有分別<br />\n邊撚唔知個讀音唔同呀？有咩討論價值呢？"},{"pid":"97a70ebf717a3fd047f9776e69ab8dcdd8a38448","tid":175894,"uid":100983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"其實一句講哂，個「挽」同「牙」字根本無「玩」同「呀」嘅意思。<br />\n讀音係會隨着時間，唔同人講而有啲改變。<br />\n好似英文，, knife, knight, knee咁，個k原本都會發埋音。經過好多年，啲人無視咗個k音。但knife嘅串法都唔會變咗做nife。<br />\n<br />\n所以玩字雖然標準發音同我地平時用開唔同，但係都無可能另一個字去代替佢。因為咁做就會失去咗文字本身嘅意思。"},{"pid":"d83667b2f8b7bb2729414a79cda40ba8e6001b93","tid":175894,"uid":619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:41:06.000Z","msg":"順手講埋個草字<br />\n出面幾百萬個post講草錢草錢都無人屌真係睇到眼火爆<br />\n就算出唔到個音起碼個儲字都啱意思，草字又唔啱音又無意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我敢講覺得挽同草啱音嗰啲一定係大陸仔廣東話都未講得正"},{"pid":"0cb1b9bb42ddea38f63d2172dc3efa11203d5422","tid":175894,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時用開速成<br />\n2個口打個唔字真係好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過牙字會睇情況用<br />\n例如我會打&quot;你仲唔訓教牙？&quot;<br />\n而唔會打&quot;你仲唔訓教呀？&quot;<br />\n但就從來無打過挽字，無乜幾何會用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牙同呀，都係2個速成碼既第一頁，一竹1，同口竹5"},{"pid":"b5c356c0c879d72ba8a760282a6bb006d4309dab","tid":175894,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:58:58.000Z","msg":"仲有果啲，搵你變左穩你，係乜撚事先會打成咁"},{"pid":"2f57a252f66f1d48199443340b6d997c453e1113","tid":175894,"uid":87550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有果啲，搵你變左穩你，係乜撚事野先會打成咁</blockquote>"},{"pid":"44a950d22072223d2f19b1f675a948a10d5123a1","tid":175894,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:02:36.000Z","msg":"香港教育都有錯<br />\n無重視過粵語<br />\n做唔到我手寫我口"},{"pid":"21b58ec29cd0c3d8a0721e68d6b624ec856fef22","tid":175894,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"啊？"},{"pid":"bf111db3a0f7dee316cc5510923e333b23288912","tid":175894,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同字讀音唔同，睇上文下理咪睇得出囉，洗鬼打讀音咩<br />\n<br />\n唔通「中間」同「中獎」個中字讀音唔同，咁就要打成 「鐘間」或者「縱獎」咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd中學雞成日話中文係死亡之卷，有無諗過其實係自己d中文水平低到仆街</blockquote><br />\ndse係考中文常識嘅就唔會死咁多人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過會死一大班5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n(香港語言學學會)\t粵音\t漢字<br />\nngaa4\t\t牙, 吾, 琊, 岈, 伢, 枒, 蚜, 衙, 芽, 玡<br />\n<br />\n(香港語言學學會)\t粵音\t漢字<br />\naa4\t\t啊<br />\n<br />\n呀\t<br />\naa1 同音字 孲, 錏, 鴉 \t\t<br />\nhaa1 同音字 颬, 蝦, 岈<br />\n<a href=\"http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhumanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk%2FLexis%2Flexi-can%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=66df07f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://humanum.arts.cuhk.edu.hk/Lexis/lexi-can/</a><br />\n<br />\n「中」字係真係有兩個讀音,<br />\n但請上面班dse中文好勁既巴打提供一下source證明呀字可以讀做「牙」</blockquote><br />\n啊"},{"pid":"f1b69ca1787b9d3499d0d866dbf48557798badfd","tid":175894,"uid":50460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:13:00.000Z","msg":"禾吊9梨牙"},{"pid":"d95d217b3f9f3d776b800c70e51e52a20ebd06b9","tid":175894,"uid":37832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"有時啲人打埋啲好好挽，系牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我心諗你噏乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學課程真係要教下啲學生寫字，唔係只會越嚟越多5p撚，佢哋有時仲會屌返人轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b93bf1225249ec266d94c689b741aac89ebddc","tid":175894,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:34:57.000Z","msg":"啊、哦、喎、呀、嗎<br />\n<br />\n口字邊係有感嘆嘅意思<br />\n<br />\n你仲未沖涼呀？<br />\n<br />\n呢句嘅意思就係：唔係呀嘛，你居然仲未沖涼？<br />\n<br />\n用個呀字係好撚正常"},{"pid":"4d61e267690ae91aa3f76cd525a49b31ad7bc0e7","tid":175894,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啊、哦、喎、呀、嗎<br />\n<br />\n口字邊係有感嘆嘅意思<br />\n<br />\n你仲未沖涼呀？<br />\n<br />\n呢句嘅意思就係：唔係呀嘛，你居然仲未沖涼？<br />\n<br />\n用個呀字係好撚正常</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a011ec86b58361fc152b6a4f24d060bc8aecff","tid":175894,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T18:15:02.000Z","msg":"嘩，冇理個post兩日原來都討論得咁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩讀唔到挽呢個問題我都明，就算音相近但換個字冇左意思成句野真係好難睇。<br />\n<br />\n但我想請教大家，究竟<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家</span>係讀玩家定挽家？我一直讀玩，但成日聽到其他人讀挽家覺得好怪，我都係照讀玩家。"},{"pid":"75c97836d71799e4d868ae8e6fa8b03f7c926e7e","tid":175894,"uid":72470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T18:25:29.000Z","msg":"你係咪玩野呀？聽到都笑撚左啦 正常都係你係咪挽野呀 ？ lm睇人繼續撐係讀前者 不過唔好比我知 我一定會笑柒你 因為你唔識廣東話"},{"pid":"5aeb94c3277cd331009707ad09f7ba7438e856ab","tid":175894,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪玩野呀？聽到都笑撚左啦 正常都係你係咪挽野呀 ？ lm睇人繼續撐係讀前者 不過唔好比我知 我一定會笑柒你 因為你唔識廣東話</blockquote><br />\n咪有巴打解釋咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 追post啦"},{"pid":"f82cf7d19a65d0ecefdef98fac8d9d9952ad4e15","tid":175894,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T20:25:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪玩野呀？聽到都笑撚左啦 正常都係你係咪挽野呀 ？ lm睇人繼續撐係讀前者 不過唔好比我知 我一定會笑柒你 因為你唔識廣東話</blockquote><br />\n廣東話文白異讀識唔識呀文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad802b812cdfd39b1815a04f65d06b4ca1932f51","tid":175894,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T21:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時用開速成<br />\n2個口打個唔字真係好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過牙字會睇情況用<br />\n例如我會打&quot;你仲唔訓教牙？&quot;<br />\n而唔會打&quot;你仲唔訓教呀？&quot;<br />\n但就從來無打過挽字，無乜幾何會用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牙你老母"},{"pid":"1c346053e1057094039a5da78e84e918b040f276","tid":175894,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T23:40:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩，冇理個post兩日原來都討論得咁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩讀唔到挽呢個問題我都明，就算音相近但換個字冇左意思成句野真係好難睇。<br />\n<br />\n但我想請教大家，究竟<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家</span>係讀玩家定挽家？我一直讀玩，但成日聽到其他人讀挽家覺得好怪，我都係照讀玩家。</blockquote><br />\n個玩字點讀都讀唔到挽嘅音<br />\n玩字有兩個音 換 同 環<br />\n後者可以變調讀做 waan2<br />\n玩家讀邊個音真係好睇你鍾意邊樣<br />\n而挽字係waan5<br />\n雖然2/5聲係有啲難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b932b6d88cc4272b8342e2e02b76b9c45d99bd","tid":175894,"uid":39693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:09:55.000Z","msg":"吾系甘牙. jpg"},{"pid":"7e324fa8a1ae71092272f6271322f41f05235a4a","tid":175894,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩，冇理個post兩日原來都討論得咁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩讀唔到挽呢個問題我都明，就算音相近但換個字冇左意思成句野真係好難睇。<br />\n<br />\n但我想請教大家，究竟<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家</span>係讀玩家定挽家？我一直讀玩，但成日聽到其他人讀挽家覺得好怪，我都係照讀玩家。</blockquote><br />\n個玩字點讀都讀唔到挽嘅音<br />\n玩字有兩個音 換 同 環<br />\n後者可以變調讀做 waan2<br />\n玩家讀邊個音真係好睇你鍾意邊樣<br />\n而挽字係waan5<br />\n雖然2/5聲係有啲難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁姐係就算劇集[幕後<span style=\"color: red;\">玩</span>家]都係食個廣東話音。姐係基本上就算公眾上玩字個音都被公認左咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de00af122d475299e16bd2c6efe6f0efbf32705","tid":175894,"uid":54918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"喂喂<br />\n依家叫你讀出黎呀?<br />\n打字就打返啱個字啦<br />\n挽你老母咩傻閪<br />\n個字嘅意思都唔撚同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fecbf13c23b21972d3edea366cee63fc5a80132","tid":175894,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4V129dY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4V129dY.jpg&h=6e218eda&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}